</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="B291B68B9E50FF806DBAF8063796C0D8" box="[199,1196,2012,2039]" pageId="7" pageNumber="438" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="FA34E5009E50FF806DBAF8063796C0D8" blockId="7.[151,1437,1076,2039]" box="[199,1196,2012,2039]" pageId="7" pageNumber="438">
<emphasis id="C8FF39129E50FF806DBAF8063274C0D8" bold="true" box="[199,334,2012,2038]" pageId="7" pageNumber="438">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name derives from Mount Kinangop where the specimen was collected.
</paragraph>
